Algorithm:-

1.  Start
2.  Declare string str
3.  Declare a function to input a string of odd number of characters
4.  declare function generate
5.  String space=" "
6.  To check that string is odd no:- if (length of string%2!=0) then execute step 7 to 30 
7.  String a,b;
8.  a=substring of str from begining to half the length
9.  b=substring of str from half to end
10. Print str string
11. Int length=length of substring a
12. int count=1(counter)
13. for(i=0;i<length;i++) loop from step 14 to 20
14. String a1=substring of a from start to length-i
15. String b1=substring of b from i to length
16. Print a1
17. for loop from 1 to count with increment of 1 per loop.Execute step 18
18. Print space
19. count=count+2
20. Print b1
21. count=count-2
22. for(int i=length-2;i>=0;i--) execute from step 23 to29
23. String a1=substring of a from start to length-i
24. String b1=substring of b from i to length
25. Print a1
26. count=count-2
27. for loop from 1 to count with increment of 1 per loop.Execute step 28
28. Print space
29. Print b1
30. Print str
31. else execute step 32 to 33
32. Print "Please Enter a word of odd Characters"
33. System.exit(0)
34. public static void main (string []args)
35. diamond obj=new diamond()
36. obj.input()
37. obj.generate()
38. End
